<br>
Now, from that information at hand, my speculation is that Valdanov and the Shade went into Akheva, and the Shade turned against Valdanov, perhaps because he knew vital information about the Akhevans. There are reports of locked chests being in Akheva. Perhaps the Shade locked Valdanov in one of the chests, and stole his journal to continue the experiments alone. Phenic later locked the Shade in the chest which is inside Nathyn's towers, forever locking away the studies of Vampyres in Lucin.<br>
<br>
